{
  "id": "adv_bond_mhk_01_05",
  "title": "miho5",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "（ここが最近話題のお化け屋敷『絶叫冥界都市』……）\n（へぇ……壁の傷とか、手が込んでるわ。プロの仕事ね）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（So this is the trending haunted house‚ \"Screaming Underworld City\"…）\n（Hmm… the scratches on the walls and everything‚ it's very detailed. Professional work.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_horror-voice-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9966.6666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、お疲れ様です\nメイク、素晴らしい出来ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ good work.\nYour makeup is wonderfully done.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.6121788023
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "（あ……。お化け役のスタッフさんに）\n（普通に挨拶してしまうなんて……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Ah…. To a staff member playing a ghost‚）\n（I just gave a normal greeting…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.6121788023,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "（こっちは仕事の下見のつもりで来たけど）\n（向こうは違うのよね。悪いことしたかしら……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I came here for a professional scouting visit‚）\n（but they're here to stay in character. Did I mess up their vibe?…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.0363043783,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.2026309329
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "（本番では、もっとリアクションを取るとして……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I'll make sure to give a better reaction during the actual shoot…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.2026309329,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4897.3704657
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.0692973612
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "きゃあああああああああああ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kyaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.0692973612,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3329.7273796000013
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.3990247408
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "っ……さすがに少し驚いたわね……貴方、大丈夫？\n……って、もしかして、すず……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… that actually startled me a bit… Are you okay?\n…Wait‚ could it be‚ Suzu…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.3990247408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.6666680652
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.3441040356
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "ひぃ！？　今度は髪の長い女の幽霊ですわーー！\nいえ、これは髪の伸びる人形の化け物！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hieee!? Now it's a long-haired woman's ghost~~!\nNo‚ is this a monster doll with growing hair?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.3441040356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.6513170877
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "誰が化け物よ。スタッフさんや、他のお客さん達の\n迷惑になるから、バタバタ走り回らないでちょうだい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Who are you calling a monster? Don't run around recklessly‚\nyou're being a nuisance to the staff and other guests.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.6513170877,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.2678475696
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "え？　mihoさん？\nま、まぁ！　mihoさんも遊びに来てましたのね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? miho-san?\nM-My‚ my! So miho-san‚ you came here to play too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.2678475696,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.1255343436
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "こ、ここ、こ、ここで会ったのも何かの縁ですし\n一緒にゴールまで行きませんこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-S-S-Since we met here‚ it must be fate‚\nso why don't we go to the exit together?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.1255343436,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.1051489192
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "なんでこんな所で貴方のおもりをしなきゃいけないのよ\n……でも、またぎゃーぎゃー騒がれてもアレね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why should I have to babysit you in a place like this?\n…Then again‚ it'll be a pain if you keep screaming and making a scene.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.1051489192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.9118157068
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "一応同じ事務所だし、悪い印象は避けないと……\nいいわ、途中の非常口までは連れて行ってあげる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're in the same agency‚ so I should avoid making a bad impression…\nFine‚ I'll take you as far as the halfway emergency exit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.9118157068,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.8277341842
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "mihoさんが遊園地で遊ぶなんて、意外ですわね\n誰と来たんですの？　あ、franさん達ですわね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's unexpected to see miho-san having fun at an amusement park.\nWho did you come with? Ah‚ it must be fran-san and the others!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.8610675175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.8004777908
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "怖気が走るようなこと言わないでちょうだい\n想像するだけで震えてくるわ。頭も痛くなってきた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please don't say such spine-chilling things.\nJust imagining it makes me shiver. Now I have a headache…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.8004777908,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_horror-voice-01.m4a",
          "delay": 15666.18887589999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.4687767983
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "あら、怖いんですの？　安心してくださいまし\nこの成宮すずがついて――ぎゃあああああああ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ are you scared? Please don't worry.\nWith this Narumiya Suzu by your side―― KYAAAAAAAA!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.4687767983,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.1333370207
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.9436061542
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "……すず、私のスカートに顔を突っ込もうとしないで\n次やったら置いていくわよ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Suzu‚ don't try to bury your face in my skirt.\nIf you do that again‚ I'm leaving you behind… got it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.9436061542,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.8828804335
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "ひいぃ！？　お化けより怖いですわ～～！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hieee!? You're scarier than the ghosts~~!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.8828804335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.8931558452
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……まさかゴールまでついてこようだなんて……\n潔く非常口から出ればいいのに、どういうつもり？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh… I can't believe you're planning to follow me to the end…\nYou could just leave through the emergency exit‚ what are you thinking?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.8931558452,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 151.1458996298
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "わ、わわ、私は遊びに来た訳ではありません。トークの\nネタに、話題のスポットを体験しに来たのですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I-I didn't come here just for fun. I came to experience\na trending spot to get material for my talk segments!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.1458996298,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 160.8638311229
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_05-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "来週の収録には、ホラー好きの方が来るそうですから\n何か一つくらいネタがあった方が盛り上がりますもの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard someone who loves horror is coming to next week's recording‚\nand it'll be more exciting if I have at least one story to tell.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.8638311229,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
